00aa1e3d879e.jpg target=_blank title="&lt;p&gt;Pavārs&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Skaits: 2093&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Atbalsta summa: 310 eiro&lt;/p&gt;"><style>//- #image-070e0476d7392f15386d3a4a2bf70f6c:before { background-image: url("https://cdntest.db.lv/lvold/10/2019/articles/2021/01/500818__600aa1e3d879e.jpg"); }</style><div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%;"><div class=stack style="position: absolute;"><div class=stack-container style="background-image: url(&quot;https://cdntest.db.lv/lvold/10/2019/articles/2021/01/500818__600aa1e3d879e.jpg&quot;); background-size: 100% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; opacity: 0.33;"></div><div class=stack-container><div class=image-contain-container id=image-070e0476d7392f15386d3a4a2bf70f6c><div class=image-contain-wrapper><img class="lazy image-contain modernize-objectfit" data-src=https://cdntest.db.lv/lvold/735/2019/articles/2021/01/500818__600aa1e3d879e.jpg style="font-family: 'object-fit: contain;'; object-fit: contain"></div></div></div></div></div></a><div class="margin-1--top text-color--darkgray"><div><span class="headline-font font-size--text-default"><p>Pavārs<br></p><p>Skaits: 2093<br></p><p>Atbalsta summa: 310 eiro</p></span></div><div><span class="headline-font font-size--text-default italic text-color--gray">Foto: pixabay.com</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=padding-4--horizontal style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><div class="container--large margin-4--top"><div class="article-base preview" id=articleBase><div style="display: flex"><div><div style="display: flex; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;"><div class=padding-4--right style="width: 180px; flex: 1 0 180px"><div class=sticky style="top: 20px; bottom: 20px"><div class="margin-2--bottom padding-2--bottom" style="border-bottom: solid 1px rgb(220,220,220);"><div><div class=padding-1--bottom style="text-align: center"><h1 class=CaslonDoric-Bold-Web style="font-size: 1.5rem">Jaunākais izdevums</h1></div><div class=padding-2--bottom><style>.latest-magazine-image { box-shadow: 0px 5px 5px 0px rgba(20,20,20,0.2); }
